title: Google\Cloud\Orchestration\Airflow\Service\V1\WebServerConfig
name: WebServerConfig
description:
The configuration settings for the Airflow web server App Engine instance.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.orchestration.airflow.service.v1.WebServerConfig

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.machine_type
params.description: Optional. Machine type on which Airflow web server is running. It has to be one of: composer-n1-webserver-2, composer-n1-webserver-4 or composer-n1-webserver-8. If not specified, composer-n1-webserver-2 will be used. Value custom is returned only in response, if Airflow web server parameters were manually changed to a non-standard values.
